    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"back in my day\"</em></p><h5 id=\"-strong-benefit-strong-\"><strong>Benefit:</strong></h5><p>You have a certain group that you just can't stand. Choose 1 clan, village, or organization. Once per turn, when you would damage a member of that group you can add 1d4 to the damage roll.</p><h5 id=\"-strong-negative-strong-\"><strong>Negative:</strong></h5><p>Your chosen group also dislikes you. Once per turn, when a member of your chosen group would damage you they add 1d4 to their damage roll.</p>",
